  <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>

  <div class="contact-info">
    <p><strong>Responsible:</strong> Dolly Ernst</p>
    <p><strong>Contact email:</strong> dollynarnjo@gmail.com</p>
    <p><strong>Last updated:</strong> August 8, 2025</p>
  </div>

  <h2>1. Data we collect</h2>
  <p>The Cafi app allows users to create coffee ratings, including:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Coffee name and origin data (planting location, brand, altitude, bean variety)</li>
    <li>Personal comments and ratings</li>
    <li>Optional coffee photos</li>
    <li>Sensory preferences (aroma, flavor, body, acidity, bitterness, intensity)</li>
    <li>Consumption preferences (with milk, espresso, cappuccino, latte macchiato, cold brew)</li>
    <li>Personal ratings (liked it, gave me energy, would buy again, good crema)</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>2. Purpose of processing</h2>
  <p>The collected data is used to:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Display, manage, and organize user's coffee ratings</li>
    <li>Allow editing and updating of existing ratings</li>
    <li>Facilitate search and filtering of coffees by name</li>
    <li>Share ratings with other users when the user decides to do so</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>3. Legal basis</h2>
  <p>Processing is based on:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>User consent when accepting the app's use</li>
    <li>Legitimate interest in the application's operation</li>
    <li>Necessity to provide the services requested by the user</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>4. Storage and retention</h2>
  <p>Data is stored locally on the user's device using Hive, a local database. Data remains on the device until:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>The user manually deletes it</li>
    <li>The user uninstalls the application</li>
    <li>The user activates synchronization features (if available)</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>5. Data sharing</h2>
  <p>The Cafi app respects your privacy:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Data is stored locally on your device</li>
    <li>Personal information is not automatically shared</li>
    <li>If you activate sharing features, only the ratings you choose are shared</li>
    <li>Personal information such as name, email, or other identifying data is not shared</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>6. User rights</h2>
  <p>As a user, you have the right to:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Access all your data stored in the app</li>
    <li>Rectify or modify your ratings at any time</li>
    <li>Delete individual ratings or all your data</li>
    <li>Export your data (if the functionality is available)</li>
  </ul>
  <p>You can exercise these rights directly from the app or by contacting <strong>dollynarnjo@gmail.com</strong>. You can also delete all your data by uninstalling the app.</p>

  <h2>7. Third-party services</h2>
  <p>This app uses:</p>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Google Play Store:</strong> For app distribution. Google may collect usage data according to their own privacy policy.</li>
    <li><strong>Hive:</strong> Local database for data storage on the device.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>8. Security</h2>
  <p>We implement security measures to protect your data:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Local encrypted storage</li>
    <li>No transmission of data to external servers</li>
    <li>Complete user control over their data</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>9. Policy changes</h2>
  <p>We reserve the right to modify this privacy policy. Any changes will be:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Published at this same web address</li>
    <li>Communicated through app updates</li>
    <li>Indicated with a new "Last updated" date</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>10. Contact</h2>
  <p>If you have questions about this privacy policy or about the processing of your data, you can contact us at:</p>
  <p><strong>Email:</strong> dollynarnjo@gmail.com</p>

  <div class="update-date">
    <p>Last updated: August 8, 2025</p>
